title: Amazon makes it harder for non-Prime members to get free delivery
description: Online shopping giant Amazon is increasing the amount that non-Prime members will have to spend to qualify for free shipping.

title: We’ve never seen a phone with a screen like this before
description: What happens when you combine an e-ink display with an Android phone? You get the new TCL 40 NXTPAPER smartphone, which is unlike anything we've seen before.

title: Gamers are finally buying new graphics cards again
description: According to the latest market figures, graphics card sales are slowly climbing back up, despite it being a traditionally weak time of the year.

title: Google now lets you know the best time to book a cheap flight
description: The latest version of Google Flights offers useful information designed to help you make a more informed choice when booking a trip.

title: MSI’s new RTX 4090 might finally convince me to buy one
description: MSI has just unveiled a slew of new graphics cards, and it appears to have done the impossible -- it turned the RTX 4090 into a normal-sized card.

title: AI drone beats pro drone racers at their own game
description: An AI drone has beaten pro drone racers at their own game in a world's first that could have implications for other drone-related tasks.
